{"tid":1631744,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"煲大黑警開槍射學生呀！！！！！！！！","createTime":"2019-10-06T16:13:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T16:58:45.000Z","uid":259963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e38f09ffe7f4e12cbc0be850d5c11d9c93d14009","tid":1631744,"uid":259963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:13:11.000Z","msg":"我係P牌都屌撚曬你班連登仔<br />\n日日係到捉三毛屌三毛<br />\n覺得裝修過份嘅直接落前線講<br />\n唔係成個熱門都屌裝修<br />\n<br />\nSolomon Yue講左話人權法案今個月簽呀<br />\n仲係到捉鬼捉三毛你地醜唔醜呀？<br />\n<br />\n見到三毛po唔該冷處理<br />\n覺得前線要改善嘅出行動po，唔撚係譴責po<br />\n<br />\n同埋<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">屌你老母黑警開實彈射中學生<br />\n<br />\n係中學生呀！！！！<br />\n<br />\n係未成年嘅中學生呀！！！！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2次呀！！！！！！！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n全撚部人仲係到屌分化！<br />\n做實事啦！<br />\nTwitter同我share所有有關依2個學生嘅新聞<br />\n無新消息都要refresh返人地呀<br />\n依2槍係幫我地過人權法案好重要嘅武器呀！"},{"pid":"f8fd700a969034c9d9a484cb4fb4e1007280dc55","tid":1631744,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:13:45.000Z","msg":"大家知唔知道宜家外國人點諗勇武<br />\n你應承過會做勇武塊盾<br />\n宜家勇武要大家backup 啊！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">勿中林鄭割蓆計！</span></strong></span><br />\n記唔記得當初應承過<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>核彈都唔割</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n正式宣布：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">文宣洗地</span></strong></span>開始［行動po求置頂］<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630198\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630198</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8d2b84377a1899b8026a3ecd509aafd0bb46ab04","tid":1631744,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:15:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>文宣國際線要你幫手</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n【行動】盡快整理所有警暴片段，同納粹暴行做對比，爭取西方實際行動支持香港<br />\n<a href=\"https:/